{"tid":1381452,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"求勇武入黎大大力屌 教下和理非點做","createTime":"2019-07-29T08:42:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T09:31:37.000Z","uid":153722,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"66700f7e0ddd94e47d5841e6cccdc578fbb8234e","tid":1381452,"uid":153722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:42:59.000Z","msg":"夢遊出過去 留係中後排<br />\n個個企係條街度 行行企企禁手機<br />\n<br />\n唔知前線僵持緊d咩<br />\n又唔知自己留係度做咩<br />\n身邊人走既走 散既散<br />\n之後 前線就有人比狗捉<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中後排直至有煙食 被驅趕 就走<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">前線係想中後排做d咩？</span></span><br />\n例如傳什麼物資比前面<br />\n<br />\n你地依家係唔係都留低咁？<br />\n可唔可以傾下 唔係為留而留<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非數量大 <br />\n好好利用會幫到手<br />\n希望前線屌之餘比意見 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7667ff1be72b8788f05ccd780c03a3d7cb57d8f6","tid":1381452,"uid":229019,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:45:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/taevSKX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtaevSKX.jpg&h=5b594017&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EExxmDh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEExxmDh.png&h=8f55259b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vF5rq4Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvF5rq4Y.jpg&h=50803fee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"880039c535f2b5c14460507646f13083bb03fe10","tid":1381452,"uid":62674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:46:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4