replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:57:36.000Z","msg":"可唔可講多d具體d<br />\n例如地袋住唔犯法既物資有咩特別缺<br />\n我地係咪要同不時自己上前問"},{"pid":"7d359b2ea9c8947dd716067d8ff6f80736a29293","tid":1381452,"uid":208452,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:57:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最基本真係送物資... 但係後埸助下陣都好 </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日(7月29)1500-1830</span></span>會有義工係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">旺角東天橋</span></span>擺街站等無上連登的市民都可以寫底感受比我地,希望大家支持<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkrevolutiondocument&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BkcGFqE5jXx4AE4DM0839cs%3D&h=8a4fa32f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkrevolutiondocument</a>"},{"pid":"edceb29ca2a4dafeb89d87d7e65c7548359523c8","tid":1381452,"uid":246884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:59:09.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n琴日勁多人喺隔離鳩企"},{"pid":"9c7fdcb107550d443ed8123f4f29f7c05ce9b119","tid":1381452,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:00:30.000Z","msg":"嗌口號，嗌個士氣返黎"},{"pid":"9e3a534d83b6c64c1792778cd6746065f2d2ea06","tid":1381452,"uid":23672,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:01:39.000Z","msg":"有前線中完催淚彈回後<br />\n如果你可以9秒9幫佢用生理鹽水沖眼<br />\n然後俾紙巾怇印乾 再幫佢手載返好晒所有野<br />\n再問佢有冇物資要換<br />\n最後講向加油<br />\n咁你就係最好既後排"},{"pid":"8e68f109bd46dff052f0e428c3d4e1cef33412ac","tid":1381452,"uid":118827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c15713557161d4119607f79cbc148b9b31069247","tid":1381452,"uid":153722,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quot